extendedInfo.description: Free Wifi! Serving Breakfast 7 days a week - We have fresh brewed hot or iced coffee from Newport Coffee Traders. Try one of our fresh baked, award winning muffins or have a hot toasted breakfast sandwich. We also have a wide selection of bagels (fresh every day from Bagelz of Wakefield), pastries, cake slices, fresh fruit and parfaits.If it's lunch you're after - how about one of our over-stuffed, made to order specialty sandwiches? It's hard to pick from our list of over 20! Be unique and build your own! There is a wide variety of deli meats & cheeses, or chicken/tuna/egg salads to choose from. Try one of our many fresh, crisp salads or hot soups of the day. You can have it all with either a 1/2 sandwich & small soup combo or 1/2 sandwich & small salad combo!Summer gets even better with the addition of our very popular New England Style Lobster Rolls and our Crab Salad Sandwiches (from May to November). Stop in, sit on our patio and look out over the beautiful Narragansett Bay!You can't pick a better spot on the Island! You'll Love Jamestown from sunrise to sunset!
